title: Looking for Friends!
body: Hey guys, looking for people to play with in ranked or in normals, or in the weekly events. I have discord and am on after work every day. Add me :) IGN: Muzzle

replies.body:
Hey Muzzle! 

I'm Huskey and I represent a large to medium sized Discord community with a heavy emphasis on League of Legends, saw your post and thought we might have what you're looking for. We do regular events, ranked team play, serious scrims, normals, arams, everything. Hope to hear from you soon! Discord link is below, join anytime!
